{"tid":1675189,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[行動] [國際文宣] 寫返個mail多謝英國上議院議員為香港發聲","createTime":"2019-10-25T16:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T10:17:38.000Z","uid":280666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"828d1954451a36e20b7f1db735031af6135b2ea6","tid":1675189,"uid":280666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:43:05.000Z","msg":"英國上議院Hong Kong Debate, 為香港人爭取公民身份, 仲一致通過<br />\n亦都有人講警暴, 同中國傾trade deal時要講香港人權問題<br />\n唔少係一聽就覺得佢地有做功課<br />\n<br />\n佢地好多個都話收到唔少香港人email<br />\n之前國際線手足做得好好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢地收到mail就做齊research幫我地發聲<br />\n我地好應該send返個thank you letter比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點send︰</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1. </span></strong><strong>email address</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.parliament.uk/mps-lords-and-offices/lords/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.parliament.uk%2Fmps-lords-and-offices%2Flords%2F&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN%2B9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=a8dc91a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.parliament.uk/mps-lords-and-offices/lords/</a><br />\n有少部份有私人email, 其餘都係得公家mailbox<br />\ncontactholmember@parliament.uk<br />\n自己係mail入面寫清楚係比邊個<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2. </span></strong>教埋你寫<strong>上款下款</strong>, 唔好錯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.parliament.uk/business/lords/whos-in-the-house-of-lords/how-to-address-a-lord/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.parliament.uk%2Fbusiness%2Flords%2Fwhos-in-the-house-of-lords%2Fhow-to-address-a-lord%2F&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN%2B9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=d3156d1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.parliament.uk/business/lords/whos-in-the-house-of-lords/how-to-address-a-lord/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">3. </span></strong>搵返條片或文字記錄, <strong>就住佢講既野多謝佢</strong>, 逐封寫<br />\n人地講明唔比bulk mail, 一式多份會直接delete<br />\n長短都冇問題<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">每人揀2,3個嚟send, 唔該晒大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">文字記錄︰</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hansard.parliament.uk/lords/2019-10-24/debates/3333A63E-9A90-4AD0-BD00-E08C13124E3B/HongKong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhansard.parliament.uk%2Flords%2F2019-10-24%2Fdebates%2F3333A63E-9A90-4AD0-BD00-E08C13124E3B%2FHongKong&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN%2B9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=6a0adb0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hansard.parliament.uk/lords/2019-10-24/debates/3333A63E-9A90-4AD0-BD00-E08C13124E3B/HongKong</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">片︰</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://parliamentlive.tv/event/index/bd83118e-cedf-4cbb-a019-13fe6ef7782a?in=14:35:35\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fparliamentlive.tv%2Fevent%2Findex%2Fbd83118e-cedf-4cbb-a019-13fe6ef7782a%3Fin%3D14%3A35%3A35&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN%2B9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=f68dc932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://parliamentlive.tv/event/index/bd83118e-cedf-4cbb-a019-13fe6ef7782a?in=14:35:35</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iOH8r3GN55Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiOH8r3GN55Y&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN%2B9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=883be40c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iOH8r3GN55Y</a><br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n題外話︰啲行動post去晒邊？"},{"pid":"8b04569a010ff616ec5034fe3311d5f2d7cc4361","tid":1675189,"uid":171259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5e6820b0897d839cb8b899faae14dbaea2ad480e","tid":1675189,"uid":269096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:55:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nALfZsW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnALfZsW.gif&h=aec21253&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qb0fZsX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqb0fZsX.jpg&h=01e2e263&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sqCevzD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsqCevzD.jpg&h=f1a1a8be&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQBCtmj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQBCtmj.jpg&h=de3c73e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UjWOz1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUjWOz1k.jpg&h=9a498ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A38mazF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA38mazF.jpg&h=0e845514&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"574ab700dd57feeea80dc2580359ac79b8913ef9","tid":1675189,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:58:57.000Z","msg":"推 但唔係好明點用..."},{"pid":"83f5249aaff30c9712926cfab7f95122c2387ebd","tid":1675189,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:32:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZUPo8oT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZUPo8oT.gif&h=0b30e983&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe94a8928dee7d996e3c4b9b0db8441fb3be9097","tid":1675189,"uid":280666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"574ab700dd57feeea80dc2580359ac79b8913ef9","tid":1675189,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T16:58:57.000Z","msg":"推 但唔係好明點用..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T19:04:56.000Z","msg":"Sorry for 1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我舉個例<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1.</strong><br />\n首先呢度就係成個討論既會議記錄<br />\n<a href=\"https://hansard.parliament.uk/lords/2019-10-24/debates/3333A63E-9A90-4AD0-BD00-E08C13124E3B/HongKong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhansard.parliament.uk%2Flords%2F2019-10-24%2Fdebates%2F3333A63E-9A90-4AD0-BD00-E08C13124E3B%2FHongKong&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN%2B9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=6a0adb0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hansard.parliament.uk/lords/2019-10-24/debates/3333A63E-9A90-4AD0-BD00-E08C13124E3B/HongKong</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2.</strong><br />\n是但揀個發言, 例如呢一位 Baroness Falkner of Margravine 既發言: <br />\n<a href=\"https://hansard.parliament.uk/lords/2019-10-24/debates/3333A63E-9A90-4AD0-BD00-E08C13124E3B/HongKong#contribution-287D8F49-5444-4C56-AF24-EF1E3DB7389B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhansard.parliament.uk%2Flords%2F2019-10-24%2Fdebates%2F3333A63E-9A90-4AD0-BD00-E08C13124E3B%2FHongKong%23contribution-287D8F49-5444-4C56-AF24-EF1E3DB7389B&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN%2B9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=4b434e6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hansard.parliament.uk/lords/2019-10-24/debates/3333A63E-9A90-4AD0-BD00-E08C13124E3B/HongKong#contribution-287D8F49-5444-4C56-AF24-EF1E3DB7389B</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJpwyjj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJpwyjj.png&h=cc356c27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢話由2014年開始支持香港抗爭<br />\n又話我地唔係為左錢同樓出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3.</strong><br />\n寫個email多謝佢<br />\n可以感謝佢支持左我地5年<br />\n同多謝佢理解我地, 明白我地唔係為錢<br />\n盡量回應返佢地講既野<br />\n( 佢地真係做足功課, 所以我想thank you letter比啲誠意, 唔好求其thank you for your support就算數 )<br />\n<br />\n<strong>4.</strong><br />\n格式, 男人用Lord, 女人用Lady<br />\n上款寫 Dear Lady Falkner of Margravine, <br />\n下款就用 Yours sincerely<br />\n<br />\n<strong>5.</strong><br />\n寫完之後, 就要搵email address啦<br />\n呢度可以search上議院議員既聯絡資料<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.parliament.uk/mps-lords-and-offices/lords/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.parliament.uk%2Fmps-lords-and-offices%2Flords%2F&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN%2B9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=a8dc91a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.parliament.uk/mps-lords-and-offices/lords/</a><br />\nclick個名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FjpHE3q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFjpHE3q.png&h=e2e0645a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n搵到 falknerk@parliament.uk<br />\n如果懶得搵<br />\n可以send去公用地址: contactholmember@parliament.uk<br />\n<br />\n<strong>6.</strong><br />\nSend<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n會議記錄好長<br />\n如果唔想睇字, 可以睇片, 兩點半打後都係, click個名會飛過去佢發言既片段<br />\n<a href=\"https://parliamentlive.tv/event/index/bd83118e-cedf-4cbb-a019-13fe6ef7782a?in=14:35:35\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fparliamentlive.tv%2Fevent%2Findex%2Fbd83118e-cedf-4cbb-a019-13fe6ef7782a%3Fin%3D14%3A35%3A35&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN%2B9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=f68dc932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://parliamentlive.tv/event/index/bd83118e-cedf-4cbb-a019-13fe6ef7782a?in=14:35:35</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SA2ev50.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSA2ev50.png&h=d0ffab70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a69f6a37870706ebffd61e747e11515b8e9d23b","tid":1675189,"uid":12824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe4a40a17babf6d1c775c4b2730c102c2ace3f4d","tid":1675189,"uid":51960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:46:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"92debf57685a45856e714468201eb7d2b57cef24","tid":1675189,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T07:44:11.000Z","msg":"記得唔好send錯人<br />\n有啲議員打毒針"},{"pid":"622068b2c4f9032a72568103788969abac5bd9d3","tid":1675189,"uid":312833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T10:17:38.000Z","msg":"支持哈薩克斯坦。<br />\n我們要支持全世界更多的自由戰士。哈薩克人抗議中國在哈薩克斯坦擴張。Chinazi是我們共同敵人。一位年輕的哈薩克人表示支持香港抗議活動，但被沉默。請在社交媒體上表達我們的支持。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/scf45279686/status/1188029668131127296\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fscf45279686%2Fstatus%2F1188029668131127296&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN%2B9%2By3EgolabMfI9ImFPBT4%3D&h=29e95a1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fscf45279686%2Fstatus%2F1188029668131127296&h=8de5a7f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/scf45279686/status/1188029668131127296</a>"}]}